title: AFL-CIO vice president to speak on campus (Southern Illinois University System)
text: ( Source : Southern Illinois University System ) October 16 , 2015 by Pete Rosenbery CARBONDALE, Ill. -- Jorge Ramirez , a leader in the nation's labor movement, will present a lecture next week at Southern Illinois University Carbondale .
